PrecisAcceptance of the transfer from the Province of Quebec of the use of a parcel of land situate in the VILLAGE OF LOURDES-DE-BLANC-SABLON, in the Township of Brest (Duplessis), that contains an area of some 2,180 square metres, which is to be used as a site for the installation of mobile homes for departmental employees (Lot 137, East Range, Rivière Blanc-Sablon).
